mods.abstract: Two color window card (black on split fountain, red to yellow) announcing George Jones and Sonny James with Tammy Wynette, Jimmy Dickens and the WXCL Country Gentlemen at the Shrine Mosque on April 13. Poster features metal photoplates of George Jones, Sonny James, Tammy Wynette and Jimmy Dickens.
